{
  "abstract": "This virus, not previously reported from India, was identified on the basis of symptoms on groundnut and Chenopodium amaranticolor and serological tests in some of the entries in an initial evaluation trial obtained from NRGC or GAU, Junagadh. Efforts are being made to determine the original source of infested seed.",
